{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/launching-google-maps-directions-link-generator/","webpackCompilationHash":"b3a30dace6f72af79829","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"blake.id","author":"Blake Wilson"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"15f9bb74-d973-557f-94ad-597f9cea08d2","excerpt":"Today, I launched Google Maps Directions Link Generator, a small web app that will generate you a “get directions” link to your company in Google Maps. I found…","html":"<p>Today, I launched Google Maps Directions Link Generator, a small web app that will generate you a “get directions” link to your company in Google Maps. I found that Google provides no simple way to get a link like this, so I decided to whip up this simple web app!</p>\n<p>It’s pretty simple and to the point. Just enter your business address/desired location, and a link will be generated for you to use on your website so customers can easily get directions to your business.</p>\n<p>Check out <a href=\"https://www.producthunt.com/posts/google-maps-directions-link-generator\">the release on Product Hunt</a>, or <a href=\"https://directionslinkgenerator.com\">go directly to the site.</a></p>\n\n  <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/ff47eabbc006369d85b08b377062adcc/626e5/directions-link-generator.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n  \n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 840px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 84.891240446796%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Directions Link Generator Home Page\" title src=\"/static/ff47eabbc006369d85b08b377062adcc/04a72/directions-link-generator.png\" srcset=\"/static/ff47eabbc006369d85b08b377062adcc/6a467/directions-link-generator.png 210w,\n/static/ff47eabbc006369d85b08b377062adcc/635b1/directions-link-generator.png 420w,\n/static/ff47eabbc006369d85b08b377062adcc/04a72/directions-link-generator.png 840w,\n/static/ff47eabbc006369d85b08b377062adcc/c6d2c/directions-link-generator.png 1260w,\n/static/ff47eabbc006369d85b08b377062adcc/27aa4/directions-link-generator.png 1680w,\n/static/ff47eabbc006369d85b08b377062adcc/626e5/directions-link-generator.png 1701w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n<p class=\"caption\">The home page of Directions Link Generator</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Launching Google Maps Directions Link Generator","date":"October 27, 2019","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/launching-google-maps-directions-link-generator/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/how-to-increase-the-tracking-speed-beyond-the-maximum-in-macos/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"How to Increase the Tracking Speed Beyond the Maximum in MacOS"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/introducing-the-jres-specification/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Introducing The Jres Specification"}}}}}